Fuel Economy of Vehicles of Different Makes (35 points)

For each vehicle class in vehicles$VClass, we plot the mean combined MPG (average of data in vehicles$comb08) for each vehicle maker every year. And then, we compute at the mean combined MPG in all years for each vehicle maker, and plot it. Both charts are created with ggplot(). Note how the vehicle makers are ranked in the second plot.
